{
  "video_id": "xsU10fX0aC0",
  "title": "To solve old problems, study new species | Alejandro Sánchez Alvarado",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Leslie Gauthier Reviewer: Camille Martínez"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12550.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "For the past few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14400.0,
      "end_time": 18369.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been spending my summers in the marine biological laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18393.0,
      "end_time": 20383.0,
      "text": "in Woods Hole, Massachusetts."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20931.0,
      "end_time": 25930.0,
      "text": "And there, what I&#39;ve been doing is essentially renting a boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25117.0,
      "end_time": 27717.0,
      "text": "What I would like to do is ask you"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27741.0,
      "end_time": 29971.0,
      "text": "to come on a boat ride with me tonight."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31836.0,
      "end_time": 36729.0,
      "text": "So, we ride off from Eel Pond into Vineyard Sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36753.0,
      "end_time": 39264.0,
      "text": "right off the coast of Martha&#39;s Vineyard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39288.0,
      "end_time": 42625.0,
      "text": "equipped with a drone to identify potential spots"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42649.0,
      "end_time": 45126.0,
      "text": "from which to peer into the Atlantic."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45150.0,
      "end_time": 48429.0,
      "text": "Earlier, I was going to say into the depths of the Atlantic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48453.0,
      "end_time": 51632.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t have to go too deep to reach the unknown."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52311.0,
      "end_time": 54882.0,
      "text": "Here, barely two miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54906.0,
      "end_time": 59452.0,
      "text": "from what is arguably the greatest marine biology lab in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59476.0,
      "end_time": 62697.0,
      "text": "we lower a simple plankton net into the water"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62721.0,
      "end_time": 64542.0,
      "text": "and bring up to the surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64566.0,
      "end_time": 67966.0,
      "text": "things that humanity rarely pays any attention to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67990.0,
      "end_time": 70521.0,
      "text": "and oftentimes has never seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74204.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s one of the organisms that we caught in our net."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74228.0,
      "end_time": 75487.0,
      "text": "This is a jellyfish."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75881.0,
      "end_time": 77193.0,
      "text": "But look closely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77217.0,
      "end_time": 80208.0,
      "text": "and living inside of this animal is another organism"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80232.0,
      "end_time": 82937.0,
      "text": "that is very likely entirely new to science."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82961.0,
      "end_time": 84639.0,
      "text": "A complete new species."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85117.0,
      "end_time": 87820.0,
      "text": "Or how about this other transparent beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87844.0,
      "end_time": 89384.0,
      "text": "with a beating heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89408.0,
      "end_time": 92836.0,
      "text": "asexually growing on top of its head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92860.0,
      "end_time": 96450.0,
      "text": "progeny that will move on to reproduce sexually."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96547.0,
      "end_time": 98330.0,
      "text": "Let me say that again:"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98580.0,
      "end_time": 101744.0,
      "text": "this animal is growing asexually on top of its head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101768.0,
      "end_time": 106255.0,
      "text": "progeny that is going to reproduce sexually in the next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106960.0,
      "end_time": 108277.0,
      "text": "A weird jellyfish?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108796.0,
      "end_time": 110106.0,
      "text": "Not quite."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110130.0,
      "end_time": 111411.0,
      "text": "This is an ascidian."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111772.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "This is a group of animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 116827.0,
      "text": "that now we know we share extensive genomic ancestry with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116851.0,
      "end_time": 121574.0,
      "text": "and it is perhaps the closest invertebrate species to our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122376.0,
      "end_time": 123745.0,
      "text": "Meet your cousin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123769.0,
      "end_time": 125199.0,
      "text": "Thalia democratica."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125223.0,
      "end_time": 127181.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127205.0,
      "end_time": 131195.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pretty sure you didn&#39;t save a spot at your last family reunion"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131219.0,
      "end_time": 132650.0,
      "text": "for Thalia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132675.0,
      "end_time": 134327.0,
      "text": "but let me tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134351.0,
      "end_time": 137679.0,
      "text": "these animals are profoundly related to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137703.0,
      "end_time": 140735.0,
      "text": "in ways that we&#39;re just beginning to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142164.0,
      "end_time": 146289.0,
      "text": "So, next time you hear anybody derisively telling you"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146313.0,
      "end_time": 150209.0,
      "text": "that this type of research is a simple fishing expedition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150234.0,
      "end_time": 153234.0,
      "text": "I hope that you&#39;ll remember the trip that we just took."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153675.0,
      "end_time": 157515.0,
      "text": "Today, many of the biological sciences only see value"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157539.0,
      "end_time": 160880.0,
      "text": "in studying deeper what we already know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160112.0,
      "end_time": 162622.0,
      "text": "in mapping already-discovered continents."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163990.0,
      "end_time": 166436.0,
      "text": "But some of us are much more interested in the unknown."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166849.0,
      "end_time": 170792.0,
      "text": "We want to discover completely new continents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170817.0,
      "end_time": 174218.0,
      "text": "and gaze at magnificent vistas of ignorance."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174674.0,
      "end_time": 178770.0,
      "text": "We crave the experience of being completely baffled"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 178794.0,
      "end_time": 180968.0,
      "text": "by something we&#39;ve never seen before."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 180992.0,
      "end_time": 182262.0,
      "text": "And yes, I agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182286.0,
      "end_time": 186860.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot of little ego satisfaction in being able to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186110.0,
      "end_time": 188585.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, I was the first one to discover that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189102.0,
      "end_time": 192700.0,
      "text": "But this is not a self-aggrandizing enterprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192310.0,
      "end_time": 194731.0,
      "text": "because in this type of discovery research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194755.0,
      "end_time": 198373.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t feel like a complete idiot most of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 198397.0,
      "end_time": 200678.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re just not sciencing hard enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200702.0,
      "end_time": 202736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204140.0,
      "end_time": 209997.0,
      "text": "So every summer I bring onto the deck of this little boat of ours"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210210.0,
      "end_time": 213438.0,
      "text": "more and more things that we know very little about."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214816.0,
      "end_time": 218304.0,
      "text": "I would like tonight to tell you a story about life"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218328.0,
      "end_time": 221668.0,
      "text": "that rarely gets told in an environment like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222915.0,
      "end_time": 228250.0,
      "text": "From the vantage point of our 21st-century biological laboratories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228274.0,
      "end_time": 232191.0,
      "text": "we have begun to illuminate many mysteries of life with knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232869.0,
      "end_time": 236506.0,
      "text": "We sense that after centuries of scientific research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236530.0,
      "end_time": 238637.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re beginning to make significant inroads"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 238661.0,
      "end_time": 242527.0,
      "text": "into understanding some of the most fundamental principles of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243223.0,
      "end_time": 248224.0,
      "text": "Our collective optimism is reflected by the growth of biotechnology"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248248.0,
      "end_time": 249522.0,
      "text": "across the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250326.0,
      "end_time": 254974.0,
      "text": "striving to utilize scientific knowledge to cure human diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255685.0,
      "end_time": 260523.0,
      "text": "Things like cancer, aging, degenerative diseases;"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260547.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264879.0,
      "text": "these are but some of the undesirables we wish to tame."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 265817.0,
      "end_time": 267261.0,
      "text": "I often wonder:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 267285.0,
      "end_time": 270446.0,
      "text": "Why is it that we are having so much trouble"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270470.0,
      "end_time": 272632.0,
      "text": "trying to solve the problem of cancer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 273960.0,
      "end_time": 276350.0,
      "text": "Is it that we&#39;re trying to solve the problem of cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276374.0,
      "end_time": 278668.0,
      "text": "and not trying to understand life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279657.0,
      "end_time": 282844.0,
      "text": "Life on this planet shares a common origin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282869.0,
      "end_time": 287922.0,
      "text": "and I can summarize 3.5 billion years of the history of life on this planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287946.0,
      "end_time": 289426.0,
      "text": "in a single slide."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289450.0,
      "end_time": 292926.0,
      "text": "What you see here are representatives of all known species in our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293321.0,
      "end_time": 296732.0,
      "text": "In this immensity of life and biodiversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 296756.0,
      "end_time": 299922.0,
      "text": "we occupy a rather unremarkable position."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299947.0,
      "end_time": 300963.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300987.0,
      "end_time": 302210.0,
      "text": "Homo sapiens."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 304621.0,
      "text": "The last of our kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 305570.0,
      "end_time": 308681.0,
      "text": "And though I don&#39;t really want to disparage at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308705.0,
      "end_time": 310676.0,
      "text": "the accomplishments of our species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310700.0,
      "end_time": 315686.0,
      "text": "as much as we wish it to be so and often pretend that it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 315710.0,
      "end_time": 318585.0,
      "text": "we are not the measure of all things."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 319311.0,
      "end_time": 322798.0,
      "text": "We are, however, the measurers of many things."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 323311.0,
      "end_time": 327560.0,
      "text": "We relentlessly quantify, analyze and compare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 327810.0,
      "end_time": 330861.0,
      "text": "and some of this is absolutely invaluable and indeed necessary."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331661.0,
      "end_time": 338480.0,
      "text": "But this emphasis today on forcing biological research to specialize"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 338720.0,
      "end_time": 340620.0,
      "text": "and to produce practical outcomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 340644.0,
      "end_time": 344198.0,
      "text": "is actually restricting our ability to interrogate life"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344222.0,
      "end_time": 348305.0,
      "text": "to unacceptably narrow confines and unsatisfying depths."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 349700.0,
      "end_time": 354480.0,
      "text": "We are measuring an astonishingly narrow sliver of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354720.0,
      "end_time": 357848.0,
      "text": "and hoping that those numbers will save all of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 358425.0,
      "end_time": 359818.0,
      "text": "How narrow do you ask?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 359842.0,
      "end_time": 361445.0,
      "text": "Well, let me give you a number."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361470.0,
      "end_time": 365989.0,
      "text": "The National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration recently estimated"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 366130.0,
      "end_time": 369940.0,
      "text": "that about 95 percent of our oceans remain unexplored."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 370674.0,
      "end_time": 372385.0,
      "text": "Now let that sink in for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 373300.0,
      "end_time": 376876.0,
      "text": "95 percent of our oceans remain unexplored."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 377712.0,
      "end_time": 379877.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s very safe to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 379901.0,
      "end_time": 384730.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t even know how much about life we do not know."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 385810.0,
      "end_time": 388735.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s not surprising that every week in my field"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 388759.0,
      "end_time": 391970.0,
      "text": "we begin to see the addition of more and more new species"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 391994.0,
      "end_time": 394253.0,
      "text": "to this amazing tree of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 394277.0,
      "end_time": 395674.0,
      "text": "This one for example --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 395698.0,
      "end_time": 397604.0,
      "text": "discovered earlier this summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 397628.0,
      "end_time": 398841.0,
      "text": "new to science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 398865.0,
      "end_time": 402157.0,
      "text": "and now occupying its lonely branch in our family tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 402973.0,
      "end_time": 404124.0,
      "text": "What is even more tragic"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 404148.0,
      "end_time": 407783.0,
      "text": "is that we know about a bunch of other species of animals out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 407807.0,
      "end_time": 411368.0,
      "text": "but their biology remains sorely under-studied."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 411392.0,
      "end_time": 413726.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure some of you have heard about the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 413750.0,
      "end_time": 417946.0,
      "text": "that a starfish can actually regenerate its arm after it&#39;s lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 417970.0,
      "end_time": 419412.0,
      "text": "But some of you might not know"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 419436.0,
      "end_time": 423784.0,
      "text": "that the arm itself can actually regenerate a complete starfish."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 424759.0,
      "end_time": 428807.0,
      "text": "And there are animals out there that do truly astounding things."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 429461.0,
      "end_time": 431171.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m almost willing to bet"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 431195.0,
      "end_time": 435514.0,
      "text": "that many of you have never heard of the flatworm, Schmidtea mediterranea."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 436423.0,
      "end_time": 438522.0,
      "text": "This little guy right here"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 438546.0,
      "end_time": 441620.0,
      "text": "does things that essentially just blow my mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 442131.0,
      "end_time": 446135.0,
      "text": "You can grab one of these animals and cut it into 18 different fragments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 446159.0,
      "end_time": 449921.0,
      "text": "and each and every one of those fragments will go on to regenerate"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 449945.0,
      "end_time": 451263.0,
      "text": "a complete animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 451287.0,
      "end_time": 452921.0,
      "text": "in under two weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453694.0,
      "end_time": 457931.0,
      "text": "18 heads, 18 bodies, 18 mysteries."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 458348.0,
      "end_time": 460744.0,
      "text": "For the past decade and a half or so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 460768.0,
      "end_time": 464477.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been trying to figure out how these little dudes do what they do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 464502.0,
      "end_time": 466701.0,
      "text": "and how they pull this magic trick off."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 466725.0,
      "end_time": 468439.0,
      "text": "But like all good magicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 468463.0,
      "end_time": 471318.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not really releasing their secrets readily to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 471342.0,
      "end_time": 472548.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 472572.0,
      "end_time": 473730.0,
      "text": "So here we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 473754.0,
      "end_time": 478209.0,
      "text": "after 20 years of essentially studying these animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 478233.0,
      "end_time": 480540.0,
      "text": "genome mapping, chin scratching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 480564.0,
      "end_time": 483783.0,
      "text": "and thousands of amputations and thousands of regenerations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 483807.0,
      "end_time": 487602.0,
      "text": "we still don&#39;t fully understand how these animals do what they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 488280.0,
      "end_time": 491624.0,
      "text": "Each planarian an ocean unto itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 491648.0,
      "end_time": 493254.0,
      "text": "full of unknowns."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494476.0,
      "end_time": 496160.0,
      "text": "One of the common characteristics"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 496184.0,
      "end_time": 498796.0,
      "text": "of all of these animals I&#39;ve been talking to you about"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 498820.0,
      "end_time": 501582.0,
      "text": "is that they did not appear to have received the memo"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 501607.0,
      "end_time": 504274.0,
      "text": "that they need to behave according to the rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504298.0,
      "end_time": 508467.0,
      "text": "that we have derived from a handful of randomly selected animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 508491.0,
      "end_time": 511212.0,
      "text": "that currently populate the vast majority"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 511237.0,
      "end_time": 513754.0,
      "text": "of biomedical laboratories across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 514116.0,
      "end_time": 516347.0,
      "text": "Meet our Nobel Prize winners."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 516371.0,
      "end_time": 518372.0,
      "text": "Seven species, essentially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 518397.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521999.00000000006,
      "text": "that have produced for us the brunt of our understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 522230.0,
      "end_time": 524490.0,
      "text": "of biological behavior today."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 525172.0,
      "end_time": 526964.0,
      "text": "This little guy right here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 526988.0,
      "end_time": 529458.0,
      "text": "three Nobel Prizes in 12 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 530204.0,
      "end_time": 532959.0,
      "text": "And yet, after all the attention they have garnered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 532984.0,
      "end_time": 535440.0,
      "text": "and all the knowledge they have generated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 535680.0,
      "end_time": 537930.0,
      "text": "as well as the lion&#39;s share of the funding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 537117.0,
      "end_time": 540990.0,
      "text": "here we are standing [before] the same litany of intractable problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 541140.0,
      "end_time": 542638.0,
      "text": "and many new challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 543220.0,
      "end_time": 545350.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because, unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 545590.0,
      "end_time": 547673.0,
      "text": "these seven animals essentially correspond"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 547697.0,
      "end_time": 554473.0,
      "text": "to 0.0009 percent of all of the species that inhabit the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 555962.0,
      "end_time": 558348.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m beginning to suspect"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 558372.0,
      "end_time": 563132.0,
      "text": "that our specialization is beginning to impede our progress at best,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 563157.0,
      "end_time": 565584.0,
      "text": "and at worst, is leading us astray."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 566235.0,
      "end_time": 569309.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because life on this planet and its history"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 569333.0,
      "end_time": 571500.0,
      "text": "is the history of rule breakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 571433.0,
      "end_time": 574780.0,
      "text": "Life started on the face of this planet as single-cell organisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 574804.0,
      "end_time": 577126.0,
      "text": "swimming for millions of years in the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 577150.0,
      "end_time": 579435.0,
      "text": "until one of those creatures decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 579460.0,
      "end_time": 581519.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m going to do things differently today;"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 581543.0,
      "end_time": 584551.0,
      "text": "today I would like to invent something called multicellularity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 584575.0,
      "end_time": 585848.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to do this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 585872.0,
      "end_time": 588524.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sure it wasn&#39;t a popular decision at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 588548.0,
      "end_time": 589575.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 589599.0,
      "end_time": 591205.0,
      "text": "but somehow, it managed to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 591229.0,
      "end_time": 593795.0,
      "text": "And then, multicellular organisms began to populate"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 593819.0,
      "end_time": 595194.0,
      "text": "all these ancestral oceans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595219.0,
      "end_time": 596407.0,
      "text": "and they thrived."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 596431.0,
      "end_time": 597964.0,
      "text": "And we have them here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 598789.0,
      "end_time": 601786.0,
      "text": "Land masses began to emerge from the surface of the oceans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 601810.0,
      "end_time": 603263.0,
      "text": "and another creature thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 603288.0,
      "end_time": 606770.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, that looks like a really nice piece of real estate."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606101.0,
      "end_time": 607352.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to move there.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 607376.0,
      "end_time": 608535.0,
      "text": "\"Are you crazy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 608559.0,
      "end_time": 611843.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to desiccate out there. Nothing can live out of water.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 611867.0,
      "end_time": 613240.0,
      "text": "But life found a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 613480.0,
      "end_time": 615371.0,
      "text": "and there are organisms now that live on land."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 615395.0,
      "end_time": 617793.0,
      "text": "Once on land, they may have looked up into the sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 617817.0,
      "end_time": 620760.0,
      "text": "and said, \"It would be nice to go to the clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 620100.0,
      "end_time": 621251.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to fly.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 621275.0,
      "end_time": 624350.0,
      "text": "\"You can&#39;t break the law of gravity, there&#39;s no way you can fly.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 624374.0,
      "end_time": 626659.0,
      "text": "And yet, nature has invented --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 626683.0,
      "end_time": 628689.0,
      "text": "multiple and independent times --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 628714.0,
      "end_time": 629921.0,
      "text": "ways to fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 630368.0,
      "end_time": 632885.0,
      "text": "I love to study these animals that break the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 632909.0,
      "end_time": 636538.0,
      "text": "because every time they break a rule, they invent something new"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 636562.0,
      "end_time": 640321.0,
      "text": "that made it possible for us to be able to be here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 640624.0,
      "end_time": 642894.0,
      "text": "These animals did not get the memo."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 642918.0,
      "end_time": 644618.0,
      "text": "They break the rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 644642.0,
      "end_time": 647437.0,
      "text": "So if we&#39;re going to study animals that break the rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 647461.0,
      "end_time": 650456.0,
      "text": "shouldn&#39;t how we study them also break the rules?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 651666.0,
      "end_time": 655540.0,
      "text": "I think we need to renew our spirit of exploration."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 655440.0,
      "end_time": 657924.0,
      "text": "Rather than bring nature into our laboratories"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 657948.0,
      "end_time": 659263.0,
      "text": "and interrogate it there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 659287.0,
      "end_time": 660993.0,
      "text": "we need to bring our science"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 661170.0,
      "end_time": 663922.0,
      "text": "into the majestic laboratory that is nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 663946.0,
      "end_time": 667857.0,
      "text": "and there, with our modern technological armamentarium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 667881.0,
      "end_time": 670707.0,
      "text": "interrogate every new form of life we find,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 670731.0,
      "end_time": 673724.0,
      "text": "and any new biological attribute that we may find."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 674486.0,
      "end_time": 678640.0,
      "text": "We actually need to bring all of our intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 678664.0,
      "end_time": 680756.0,
      "text": "to becoming stupid again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 680780.0,
      "end_time": 684639.0,
      "text": "clueless [before] the immensity of the unknown."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 685116.0,
      "end_time": 686477.0,
      "text": "Because after all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 686501.0,
      "end_time": 688660.0,
      "text": "science is not really about knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 688684.0,
      "end_time": 691425.0,
      "text": "Science is about ignorance."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 691449.0,
      "end_time": 692814.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 692838.0,
      "end_time": 695968.0,
      "text": "Once, Antoine de Saint-Exupéry wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 695993.0,
      "end_time": 697794.0,
      "text": "\"If you want to build a ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 697818.0,
      "end_time": 699762.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t drum up people to collect wood"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 699786.0,
      "end_time": 702880.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t assign them tasks and work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 702112.0,
      "end_time": 706206.0,
      "text": "but rather teach them to long for the endless immensity of the sea ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 706646.0,
      "end_time": 708349.0,
      "text": "As a scientist and a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 708374.0,
      "end_time": 710335.0,
      "text": "I like to paraphrase this to read"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 710359.0,
      "end_time": 713517.0,
      "text": "that we scientists need to teach our students"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 713541.0,
      "end_time": 715992.0,
      "text": "to long for the endless immensity of the sea"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 716160.0,
      "end_time": 717453.0,
      "text": "that is our ignorance."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 718768.0,
      "end_time": 722633.0,
      "text": "We Homo sapiens are the only species we know of"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 722657.0,
      "end_time": 725930.0,
      "text": "that is driven to scientific inquiry."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 725645.0,
      "end_time": 727779.0,
      "text": "We, like all other species on this planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 727803.0,
      "end_time": 732294.0,
      "text": "are inextricably woven into the history of life on this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 732989.0,
      "end_time": 736156.0,
      "text": "And I think I&#39;m a little wrong when I say that life is a mystery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 736180.0,
      "end_time": 738891.0,
      "text": "because I think that life is actually an open secret"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 738915.0,
      "end_time": 742899.0,
      "text": "that has been beckoning our species for millennia to understand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 743344.0,
      "end_time": 744945.0,
      "text": "So I ask you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 744969.0,
      "end_time": 748742.0,
      "text": "Aren&#39;t we the best chance that life has to know itself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 749530.0,
      "end_time": 750204.0,
      "text": "And if so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 750228.0,
      "end_time": 751958.0,
      "text": "what the heck are we waiting for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 752368.0,
      "end_time": 753569.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 753593.0,
      "end_time": 756847.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}